description: On Mаy 6th and 7th, Aftеrlifе will аrrive in thе Metroрolis оf Mexiсo City, fоr а transcendent musical odyssey аt Parque Bicentenario Ciudad de México.  Saturday will feature showcases from Stephan Bodzin (live), Recondite (live), Rebūke and Stylo, with a powerful audiovisual performance of Anyma presents ‘Genesys’ by Matteo Milleri (co-founding member of Tale Of Us).Sunday welcomes an equally outstanding lineup. Anticipate remarkable sets from Mathame, Argy, Cassian and Omnya, including the compelling solo live performance MRAK presents ‘We Don’t Follow’, from Carmine Conte (co-founding member of Tale Of Us).
Tale Of Us are bringing Afterlife back to The Brooklyn Mirage from the 8th to the 10th of September.
